296
00:18:52,190 --> 00:18:56,220
[Sanjiangkou People's Hospital]

297
00:18:56,290 --> 00:19:00,170
[Orthopaedics Department] [Orthopaedics Section 1]

298
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:59,160
My leg got hurt.
What are you crying out for?

299
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,000
Well, you...

300
00:19:00,310 --> 00:19:00,840
Here.

301
00:19:00,960 --> 00:19:01,480
Okay.

302
00:19:01,720 --> 00:19:02,350
I'm fine.

303
00:19:02,350 --> 00:19:03,280
I'm really fine.

304
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,070
Have a seat.

305
00:19:06,220 --> 00:19:14,210
[Orthopaedics Department] [Orthopaedics Section 1]

306
00:19:06,510 --> 00:19:07,160
Please wait a moment.

307
00:19:07,160 --> 00:19:07,750
I'll go get the X-rays.

308
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:08,280
Go ahead.

309
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:40,110
Hello.

310
00:19:40,480 --> 00:19:41,280
Hello, Chief.

311
00:19:41,510 --> 00:19:42,650
Li Feng has confessed to everything.

312
00:19:42,650 --> 00:19:43,710
Confessed to what?

313
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:44,720
This Li Feng,

314
00:19:44,840 --> 00:19:46,300
over the past three years,

315
00:19:46,310 --> 00:19:48,440
has committed over a dozen robberies.

316
00:19:48,510 --> 00:19:49,790
Among them, nine involved murder,

317
00:19:49,790 --> 00:19:50,750
one attempted murder,

318
00:19:50,750 --> 00:19:52,640
resulting in fifteen deaths in total.

319
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:54,510
He started to hide in Sanjiangkou
half a year ago.

320
00:19:54,510 --> 00:19:55,440
How many deaths?

321
00:19:55,480 --> 00:19:56,270
Fifteen.

322
00:19:57,610 --> 00:19:58,260
Chief.

323
00:19:58,480 --> 00:20:00,360
He is a Class A wanted criminal.

324
00:20:00,380 --> 00:20:01,680
For three consecutive years,

325
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:02,480
the bureau has issued

326
00:20:02,480 --> 00:20:04,030
a priority arrest warrant for him.

327
00:20:04,030 --> 00:20:04,640
Across five provinces,

328
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:07,070
tens of thousands of police officers
have been deployed to catch him.

329
00:20:07,070 --> 00:20:07,680
Several times,

330
00:20:07,680 --> 00:20:09,010
he was almost caught.

331
00:20:09,660 --> 00:20:10,580
So close.

332
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:12,720
But he managed to escape every time.

333
00:20:12,720 --> 00:20:13,430
This time,

334
00:20:13,550 --> 00:20:15,380
you finally caught him.

335
00:20:24,310 --> 00:20:24,790
Chief?

336
00:20:25,550 --> 00:20:27,010
Chief, are you listening?

337
00:20:27,330 --> 00:20:29,820
[Orthopaedics Department] [Orthopaedics Section 1]

338
00:20:27,920 --> 00:20:29,160
Are you sure it's him?

339
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:30,880
The fingerprints match.

340
00:20:30,880 --> 00:20:31,880
There's no doubt.

341
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:33,350
The interrogation is still ongoing.

342
00:20:33,350 --> 00:20:35,000
Chief Qi and Captain Wang
are both keeping an eye on it.

343
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:35,660
Good. Then,

344
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:37,310
thanks for your hard work.

345
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:39,110
Keep interrogating him for now.

346
00:20:40,570 --> 00:20:43,040
[Interrogation Room]

347
00:20:43,080 --> 00:20:46,420
[Orthopedic Section 1]

348
00:20:47,030 --> 00:20:48,690
That's quite an achievement.

349
00:20:49,690 --> 00:20:50,480
This is a year ahead of schedule,

350
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:52,340
and I've overfulfilled the task.

351
00:20:53,680 --> 00:20:56,680
Does this mean
I can go back to the provincial capital?

352
00:21:04,830 --> 00:21:05,350
Chief.

353
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:08,840
Chief.

354
00:21:08,890 --> 00:21:09,840
Why are you standing up?

355
00:21:09,840 --> 00:21:10,350
Well.

356
00:21:10,720 --> 00:21:11,440
I was just sitting here,

357
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:12,170
and suddenly

358
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,920
my whole leg cannot be felt.

359
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:14,520
It's numb.

360
00:21:15,780 --> 00:21:16,930
Is it that serious?

361
00:21:19,590 --> 00:21:20,160
Look,

362
00:21:20,590 --> 00:21:21,850
I really can't feel it.

363
00:21:27,720 --> 00:21:29,780
You have to keep taking the medicine.

364
00:21:30,310 --> 00:21:31,040
And you

365
00:21:31,550 --> 00:21:32,810
should stay positive.

366
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:34,020
In your daily life,

367
00:21:34,350 --> 00:21:35,920
watch more funny jokes,

368
00:21:36,310 --> 00:21:38,180
cross-talks, sketches,

369
00:21:38,270 --> 00:21:39,270
or comedy movies.

370
00:21:41,640 --> 00:21:43,040
He's been watching them.

371
00:21:47,920 --> 00:21:49,410
Your vital signs

372
00:21:49,880 --> 00:21:51,080
are all quite stable.

373
00:21:51,790 --> 00:21:54,120
Do you feel uncomfortable anywhere else?

374
00:21:57,200 --> 00:21:57,810
It hurts.

375
00:21:58,400 --> 00:21:59,330
What did you say?

376
00:22:00,720 --> 00:22:01,250
It hurts.

377
00:22:03,270 --> 00:22:04,160
Speak louder.

378
00:22:04,200 --> 00:22:05,590
My arm hurts!

379
00:22:10,680 --> 00:22:11,160
Arm.

380
00:22:14,590 --> 00:22:16,100
His arm hurts.

381
00:22:16,510 --> 00:22:17,040
How about

382
00:22:17,110 --> 00:22:19,370
you take him to orthopedics downstairs?

383
00:22:19,590 --> 00:22:20,030
Okay.

384
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:24,880
Doctor,

385
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:26,380
is he okay?

386
00:22:28,030 --> 00:22:29,090
His bones are fine.

387
00:22:29,310 --> 00:22:30,400
I'll just prescribe some medicine for him.

388
00:22:30,400 --> 00:22:30,980
Okay.

389
00:22:33,440 --> 00:22:34,500
Then could there be

390
00:22:34,890 --> 00:22:36,240
some neurological problem?

391
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:37,880
Right now, not only
does my whole leg hurt,

392
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:38,740
it's also numb.

393
00:22:40,110 --> 00:22:41,440
How about I get one of those

394
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,400
full body checkups

395
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:44,060
to examine my body carefully?

396
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:46,070
Theoretically, it's not necessary.

397
00:22:46,070 --> 00:22:47,550
I don't think it's anything serious.

398
00:22:47,550 --> 00:22:48,310
Don't you trust

399
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:49,510
what the doctor says?

400
00:22:49,790 --> 00:22:51,030
She said theoretically.

401
00:22:51,030 --> 00:22:52,830
But my whole leg actually hurts.

402
00:22:53,240 --> 00:22:53,960
How about I go back to

403
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:55,030
the provincial hospital for a checkup.

404
00:22:55,030 --> 00:22:56,480
After all, the medical facilities here...

405
00:22:56,210 --> 00:22:56,530
[Sanjiangkou People's Hospital Radiology Report]

406
00:22:56,720 --> 00:22:58,510
If you don't trust our hospital,

407
00:22:58,510 --> 00:22:59,910
you can go to another one.

408
00:23:02,840 --> 00:23:03,900
Are you his family?

409
00:23:04,510 --> 00:23:05,220
How about

410
00:23:05,420 --> 00:23:07,110
you take him to the fourth floor?

411
00:23:07,110 --> 00:23:08,160
The psychiatry department

412
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:10,020
might be able to cure his illness.

413
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:16,540
[Psychiatry Department]

414
00:23:18,000 --> 00:23:19,260
Mr. Rong, are you okay?

415
00:23:21,890 --> 00:23:23,420
Tell Bowen to come to see me.

416
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:25,670
No need.

417
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:27,880
We'll go find him.

418
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:30,770
Bring your weapons.

419
00:23:33,160 --> 00:23:33,720
Mr. Rong.

420
00:23:34,790 --> 00:23:36,250
Are you suspecting that Ye

421
00:23:36,860 --> 00:23:38,340
was killed by Bowen?

422
00:23:42,110 --> 00:23:43,640
Killing someone

423
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:45,160
isn't easy for an ordinary person,

424
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:46,690
let alone killing another.

425
00:23:48,830 --> 00:23:50,520
On the birthday, I told Bowen

426
00:23:50,550 --> 00:23:51,910
to clean up his mess,

427
00:23:52,270 --> 00:23:53,880
or Ye wouldn't show mercy.

428
00:23:55,070 --> 00:23:56,130
Then Ye was killed.

429
00:23:57,310 --> 00:23:57,920
Who else

430
00:23:57,940 --> 00:23:59,340
could I suspect for this?

431
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:01,280
If it really is him,

432
00:24:01,830 --> 00:24:03,630
I'll have to clean house myself.

433
00:24:04,400 --> 00:24:05,690
If he dares to hurt Ye,

434
00:24:06,160 --> 00:24:08,220
he'll dare to hurt me sooner or later.

435
00:24:16,240 --> 00:24:20,690
[Psychiatry Department]

436
00:24:16,410 --> 00:24:17,920
Why are we on the fourth floor?

437
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:18,590
Didn't the doctor ask you

438
00:24:18,590 --> 00:24:20,920
to come to the fourth floor
for a check-up?

439
00:24:27,070 --> 00:24:27,870
Xing, tell me,

440
00:24:28,570 --> 00:24:29,830
do I look like a psycho?

441
00:24:31,070 --> 00:24:31,680
Didn't you say

442
00:24:31,680 --> 00:24:33,070
you want a full checkup?

443
00:24:39,310 --> 00:24:40,760
Killing 15 people.

444
00:24:41,070 --> 00:24:43,530
How many times
would he be executed for that?

445
00:24:43,550 --> 00:24:45,010
Let's not talk about work.

446
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:47,210
You have all kinds of experiences.

447
00:24:47,210 --> 00:24:49,140
I still have a lot to learn from you.

448
00:25:01,440 --> 00:25:02,030
Seriously, do people nowadays

449
00:25:02,030 --> 00:25:03,290
really brag that much?

450
00:25:03,510 --> 00:25:04,510
Just ignore them.

451
00:25:05,240 --> 00:25:06,720
They were going to the fourth floor.

452
00:25:06,720 --> 00:25:07,980
They might be psychos.

453
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:11,810
I just came down from the fourth floor.

454
00:25:12,880 --> 00:25:13,410
Mr. Rong.

455
00:25:14,030 --> 00:25:16,000
I definitely wasn't talking about you.

456
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:17,480
Then why come to orthopedics?

457
00:25:17,480 --> 00:25:18,590
Didn't the doctor just ask us to

458
00:25:18,590 --> 00:25:20,310
come to orthopedics on the second floor?

459
00:25:20,310 --> 00:25:21,690
Why come to orthopedics?

460
00:25:21,260 --> 00:25:23,590
[Orthopedics Department]

461
00:25:21,790 --> 00:25:23,000
Since we're here, let's have a check-up.

462
00:25:23,000 --> 00:25:23,350
No, no.

463
00:25:23,350 --> 00:25:24,200
Let's have a thorough check-up.

464
00:25:23,660 --> 00:25:24,690
[Orthopedics Section 2]

465
00:25:24,200 --> 00:25:24,930
No, I refuse.

466
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:30,920
Even if one really killed 15 people,

467
00:25:32,310 --> 00:25:34,170
he can only be shot once if caught.

468
00:25:43,310 --> 00:25:43,900
Li Feng.

469
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:46,810
Start confessing from the first case.

470
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:48,880
Can I start confessing

471
00:25:48,880 --> 00:25:50,080
from the second case?

472
00:25:50,240 --> 00:25:51,640
Mind your attitude.

473
00:25:52,930 --> 00:25:54,620
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau Personal Information Form]

474
00:25:55,110 --> 00:25:56,150
You and Li Feng

475
00:25:56,180 --> 00:25:57,710
grew up in the same village.

476
00:25:57,960 --> 00:25:59,480
You are one year younger than him,

477
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:01,210
so you were childhood friends.

478
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:02,810
When you were 16,

479
00:26:03,030 --> 00:26:05,830
you were raped by your uncle
from the same village.

480
00:26:06,030 --> 00:26:07,830
He was a villain in your village.

481
00:26:08,310 --> 00:26:10,310
Your parents were threatened by him

482
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:11,930
and didn't dare to speak up.

483
00:26:12,270 --> 00:26:13,330
After Li Feng found out,

484
00:26:13,330 --> 00:26:15,190
he went to him to settle the score.

485
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:16,480
During the fight,

486
00:26:17,190 --> 00:26:18,790
he accidentally killed him.

487
00:26:19,750 --> 00:26:21,880
He was sentenced to 12 years in prison.

488
00:26:22,070 --> 00:26:22,920
This is the

489
00:26:22,920 --> 00:26:24,380
first crime he committed.

490
00:26:25,200 --> 00:26:26,070
I killed people

491
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:28,680
because fate was

492
00:26:28,680 --> 00:26:29,880
too unfair to my wife.

493
00:26:30,160 --> 00:26:31,360
After I was released,

494
00:26:31,750 --> 00:26:34,410
I found out
she was forced to marry someone else.

495
00:26:34,510 --> 00:26:36,240
That jerk didn't love her at all.

496
00:26:35,080 --> 00:26:42,900
♪ The moon is hanging far away in the night ♪

497
00:26:37,170 --> 00:26:39,100
After finding out she was raped,

498
00:26:39,310 --> 00:26:40,840
not only did he not help her,

499
00:26:40,960 --> 00:26:43,400
but he also beat her constantly.

500
00:26:43,830 --> 00:26:45,270
He forced her to do that

501
00:26:44,230 --> 00:26:50,700
♪ Lighting up the pedestrians' faces ♪

502
00:26:45,880 --> 00:26:46,960
to support him.

503
00:26:48,350 --> 00:26:50,720
In a fit of rage, I killed his whole family.

504
00:26:50,760 --> 00:26:52,090
They were all scumbags.

505
00:26:52,740 --> 00:26:59,080
♪ Why are you standing in the center of the city? ♪

506
00:26:53,700 --> 00:26:55,200
Then I let her elope with me.

507
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:57,110
Li Feng constantly committed robberies

508
00:26:57,110 --> 00:26:57,950
and thefts

509
00:26:58,070 --> 00:26:59,030
to make a living.

510
00:26:59,920 --> 00:27:00,880
During the time, he killed

511
00:27:00,090 --> 00:27:07,220
♪ But I couldn't find my way home ♪

512
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:02,410
multiple innocent people.

513
00:27:05,110 --> 00:27:06,270
Besides these 15 lives,

514
00:27:06,270 --> 00:27:07,470
are there any others?

515
00:27:15,550 --> 00:27:16,030
No.

516
00:27:16,830 --> 00:27:18,440
Let me ask you another question.

517
00:27:18,440 --> 00:27:18,920
Li Feng,

518
00:27:19,030 --> 00:27:20,890
you were doing fine in Jiangsu,

519
00:27:20,960 --> 00:27:22,400
and the police didn't track you down.

520
00:27:22,400 --> 00:27:23,960
Why did you come to Sanjiangkou?

521
00:27:23,960 --> 00:27:25,160
To hide from you guys.

522
00:27:27,830 --> 00:27:28,420
Half a year ago,

523
00:27:28,420 --> 00:27:29,750
we came to Sanjiangkou.

524
00:27:31,110 --> 00:27:33,040
Then we didn't want to run anymore,

525
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:36,310
so we took over a small shop
and settled down.

526
00:27:36,310 --> 00:27:37,440
One day, on the street,

527
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:38,900
I ran into an old cellmate.

528
00:27:39,750 --> 00:27:41,240
He said someone hired him to kill a person.

529
00:27:41,240 --> 00:27:43,000
The remuneration was 200,000 yuan.

530
00:27:43,000 --> 00:27:44,440
He wanted my help and promised

531
00:27:44,440 --> 00:27:45,830
to give me half of the money.

532
00:27:45,830 --> 00:27:46,550
So I agreed.

533
00:27:48,640 --> 00:27:49,840
I only found out later

534
00:27:50,030 --> 00:27:51,270
that the target

535
00:27:52,350 --> 00:27:53,440
was an old cop.

536
00:27:53,920 --> 00:27:54,680
A cop?

537
00:27:54,750 --> 00:27:56,830
Seemed like he was a superior official.

538
00:27:56,830 --> 00:27:57,880
What was his name?

539
00:27:59,200 --> 00:28:00,200
I don't remember.

540
00:28:01,640 --> 00:28:02,350
I think...

541
00:28:04,240 --> 00:28:05,770
I think his last name was Lu.

542
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:08,790
Chief Qi.

543
00:28:10,590 --> 00:28:11,990
Keep interrogating him.

544
00:28:13,590 --> 00:28:14,030
Show him the photo.

545
00:28:14,030 --> 00:28:14,360
Okay.

546
00:28:15,160 --> 00:28:16,000
Because of my leg injury,

547
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:16,960
I might need to go back to...

548
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:17,910
Sit down first, Yi'ang.

549
00:28:17,910 --> 00:28:18,460
Sit.

550
00:28:20,000 --> 00:28:20,800
What's wrong?

551
00:28:29,750 --> 00:28:30,680
Is he the target?

552
00:28:38,110 --> 00:28:38,550
Yes.

553
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:41,240
And then?

554
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:43,450
Did you do it?

555
00:28:43,680 --> 00:28:44,110
No.

556
00:28:44,960 --> 00:28:46,020
I wanted to at first

557
00:28:46,640 --> 00:28:47,590
because my child is too young,

558
00:28:47,590 --> 00:28:49,270
and I would need
a lot of money in the future.

559
00:28:49,270 --> 00:28:50,930
I thought if I did this one job,

560
00:28:51,350 --> 00:28:52,590
even if I got caught,

561
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:54,780
it'd be good to leave them some money.

562
00:28:55,750 --> 00:28:57,610
Later, my wife talked me out of it.

563
00:28:58,030 --> 00:28:58,760
Afterwards,

564
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:00,480
I went soft.

565
00:29:01,440 --> 00:29:02,160
My cellmate

566
00:29:02,160 --> 00:29:04,020
never contacted me again either.

567
00:29:05,590 --> 00:29:07,130
Was this cop named Lu

568
00:29:07,250 --> 00:29:08,320
killed later?

569
00:29:09,790 --> 00:29:11,590
I wasn't involved. I don't know.

570
00:29:11,830 --> 00:29:12,590
But I guess

571
00:29:12,590 --> 00:29:13,990
my cellmate didn't do it.

572
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:15,730
He didn't have the guts.

573
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:18,580
What's your cellmate's name?

574
00:29:21,510 --> 00:29:22,200
If you don't know his name,

575
00:29:22,200 --> 00:29:23,530
how about his nickname?

576
00:29:23,550 --> 00:29:25,410
Where did he live in Sanjiangkou?

577
00:29:27,110 --> 00:29:27,920
Sir,

578
00:29:29,160 --> 00:29:30,400
is the answer to this question

579
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:31,770
important to you?

580
00:29:33,720 --> 00:29:34,350
Li Feng.

581
00:29:35,440 --> 00:29:36,240
Look at me.

582
00:29:37,750 --> 00:29:38,830
I'm asking you one last time.

583
00:29:38,830 --> 00:29:39,830
Speak properly.

584
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:44,300
